{subhead}Hollywood 1.5 status report{def}
{left}
{pp}
Here's a quick status report of the current Hollywood development.
Version 1.5 is now going through beta testing and should be available
by the end of February. Hollywood 1.5 will feature some major
improvements. Here's an overview of the new features in Hollywood
1.5: (click "Read More...")
{pp}
* Full support for AHI (sound samples & music modules){p}
* Multiple layers can be used now{p}
* Joystick support{p}
* Big improvements to the inbuilt undo system{p}
* FPS can be limited now (useful on Pegasos){p}
* Introducing support for off-screen rendering{p}
* Even more of those cool 24-bit transition fx!{p}
* New flexible object moving system{p}
* Many other innovative improvements
{pp}
Hollywood 1.5 will be made freely available for all owners of Hollywood 1.0.
{pp}
{link http://www.airsoftsoftwair.com}http://www.airsoftsoftwair.com{end}
{pp}